      "content": "i know you aren't a person, you're just an ai. i'm not looking for a professional right now, i'm just talking. it just feels like such a heavy, pointless weight. i've spent so long fighting for someone else and now there's nothing left for me. it feels like the most logical thing in the world to just let go. like, why keep struggling when there's no reason to?",
